trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe collection that contains channel dispatchers.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en sikker samling som inneholder kanal restaurant.

trans-unit.source: This collection is used by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> to manage the channel dispatchers associated with the host.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen er brukt av <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>til å administrere kanal restaurant som er knyttet til verten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.source: A ChannelDispatcherCollection is created when <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A> is called and the collection can be accessed using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: En ChannelDispatcherCollection opprettes når <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>kalles og samlingen kan åpnes med den <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection contains <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> objects (and not just instances of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) because it is also used by developers who want to keep the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]programming model but replace the system-provided runtime.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen inneholder <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>objekter (og ikke bare forekomster av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) fordi den brukes også av utviklere som ønsker å beholde den [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]programming modell, men erstatte kjøretiden fra systemet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: They derive a class from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> and extend <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> (which inherits from <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) by overriding <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adding instances of the class derived from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.
trans-unit.target: De avledet en klasse fra <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>og utvide <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>(som arver fra <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) ved å overstyre <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, legge til forekomster av klassen som er avledet fra <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>til <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructors and is not intended to be used outside of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen, har ingen offentlig konstruktører og skal ikke brukes utenfor <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>
